      "path": "README.md",
      "content": "# Payment Validation Service\n\nSpring Boot 3.x microservice migrated from a legacy SOA composite/BPEL/WSDL/XSD contract.\n\n## Business Summary\n- Accepts a payment validation request\n- Validates required fields and amount\n- Calls downstream AccountValidationService\n- Returns APPROVED or REJECTED response\n\n## SOA Mapping\n- `receive` -> REST controller endpoint\n- `assign` -> service validation and mapping logic\n- `invoke` -> downstream WebClient call\n- `reply` -> REST response\n- XSD request element -> `PaymentValidationRequest` DTO\n- WSDL operation `validatePayment` -> `POST /api/payments/validate`\n\n## Endpoint\n### POST /api/payments/validate\n\nRequest:\n```json\n{\n  \"paymentReference\": \"REF-1001\",\n  \"paymentType\": \"CARD\",\n  \"amount\": 150.0\n}\n```\n\nResponse:\n```json\n{\n  \"paymentReference\": \"REF-1001\",\n  \"paymentType\": \"CARD\",\n  \"amount\": 150.0,\n  \"status\": \"APPROVED\",\n  \"message\": \"Payment validated successfully\"\n}\n```\n\n## Run Locally\n```bash\n./gradlew bootRun\n```\n\n## Build\n```bash\n./gradlew clean bootJar\n```\n\n## Docker\nBuild image:\n```bash\ndocker build -t payment-validation-service .\n```\n\nRun container:\n```bash\ndocker run -p 8080:8080 payment-validation-service\n```\n\n## Notes\n- Downstream account validation base URL is configurable via `downstream.account-validation.base-url`\n- Default downstream URL: `http://localhost:8081`\n- Includes global exception handling for validation and downstream failures\n"
